#: .\arborist\templates\arborist\faq.html:32
msgid "Frequently Asked Questions"
msgstr ""

#: .\arborist\templates\arborist\faq.html:35
msgid "Answers to the most important questions about tree care."
msgstr ""

#: .\arborist\templates\arborist\faq.html:59 .\arborist\views.py:284
msgid "How much does a tree inspection cost?"
msgstr ""

#: .\arborist\templates\arborist\faq.html:62 .\arborist\views.py:286
msgid ""
"The cost of a tree inspection depends on the number of trees and the effort "
"required. Contact me for an individual quote."
msgstr ""

#: .\arborist\templates\arborist\faq.html:67 .\arborist\views.py:291
msgid "When is the best time for fruit tree pruning?"
msgstr ""

#: .\arborist\templates\arborist\faq.html:70
msgid ""
"The best time for fruit tree pruning varies by fruit type. Pome fruit "
"(apple, pear) is usually pruned in winter, stone fruit (cherry, plum) after "
"harvest in summer."
msgstr ""

#: .\arborist\templates\arborist\faq.html:75 .\arborist\views.py:299
msgid "Do you also work with rope climbing technique?"
msgstr ""

#: .\arborist\templates\arborist\faq.html:78 .\arborist\views.py:301
msgid ""
"Yes, I am SKT-B certified and work with professional rope climbing "
"technique. This enables tree-friendly care even without heavy machinery."
msgstr ""

#: .\arborist\templates\arborist\faq.html:83 .\arborist\views.py:307
msgid "In which regions do you operate?"
msgstr ""

#: .\arborist\templates\arborist\faq.html:86 .\arborist\views.py:309
msgid ""
"I operate throughout Luxembourg, with a focus on the center and south of the "
"country."
msgstr ""

#: .\arborist\templates\arborist\faq.html:91 .\arborist\views.py:314
msgid "Do you also offer emergency services?"
msgstr ""

#: .\arborist\templates\arborist\faq.html:94
msgid ""
"Yes, for storm damage or other emergencies I am also available on short "
"notice. Contact me by phone for urgent requests."
msgstr ""

#: .\arborist\templates\arborist\faq.html:108
msgid "More Frequently Asked Questions"
msgstr ""

#: .\arborist\templates\arborist\faq.html:114
msgid "Do I need a permit for tree removal?"
msgstr ""

#: .\arborist\templates\arborist\faq.html:117
msgid ""
"In many municipalities in Luxembourg, tree removal requires a permit. I am "
"happy to advise you on local regulations and help with the application "
"process."
msgstr ""

#: .\arborist\templates\arborist\faq.html:123
msgid "What is the difference between tree care and tree inspection?"
msgstr ""

#: .\arborist\templates\arborist\faq.html:126
msgid ""
"Tree inspection is the systematic examination of a tree for damage and "
"traffic safety. Tree care includes active measures such as pruning, deadwood "
"removal, and crown correction."
msgstr ""

#: .\arborist\templates\arborist\faq.html:132
msgid "How often should a tree be inspected?"
msgstr ""

#: .\arborist\templates\arborist\faq.html:135
msgid ""
"For trees in high-traffic locations, the FLL recommends annual inspection. "
"For less frequented locations, a longer interval may be sufficient."
msgstr ""

#: .\arborist\templates\arborist\faq.html:141
msgid "Do you dispose of the cuttings?"
msgstr ""

#: .\arborist\templates\arborist\faq.html:144
msgid ""
"Yes, upon request I dispose of the cuttings properly. Alternatively, they "
"can remain on-site, e.g., as wood chips for your garden beds."
msgstr ""

#: .\arborist\templates\arborist\faq.html:156
msgid "More Questions?"
msgstr ""

#: .\arborist\templates\arborist\faq.html:159
msgid "Contact me - I am happy to answer all your questions about tree care."
msgstr ""

